Package: fastpos
Type: Package
Title: Finds the critical sequential point of stability for a Pearson correlation
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2019-04-17
Authors@R: person("Johannes", "Titz", email = "johannes.titz@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Finds the critical sample size ("point of stability") for a 
    correlation to stabilize in Schoenbrodt and Perugini's definition of 
    sequential stability.
